First software crisisï¼š

1960s to 1970sï¼Œassembly language to C lanuage to solve **large-scale production problem.**

Secord software crisisï¼š

1980s to 1990sï¼Œprocess-oritend to object-oritend to solve **ever-increasing complexity of large software.**

Engineering thinking or software engineering is about addressing **the ever-increasing demands and complexity.**

